         ShowEQ dosn't show a mob's total helth... the only data given to your client is percentages of health.</P><P>Do one damage and he's at 99% health.  Don't assume it's a full percent with all the damage they did.  Kerafyrm could have had 2 billion health or a trillion health.  Hey, I could get him to 99% health solo.  By the way, there are no level 60 mobs in ST.  They are all 63+ besides one that cons yellow and some level 45 mobs.  I'm not very familiar with ST pre wakeing but if it's anything like it is now, no mobs would be up besides one wandering mob that dosn't get in the way and 2 next to the drop down that are not in aggro range.  SkyShrine would be where the real damage would be done.</P><P><A href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26159">Reegor</A> Mortees<BR>scaled Warlock<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
